What a year this has been for @chapkisdance @chapkisdancestudio! We are so grateful for every single dancer that’s a part of our big dance family and so blessed and thankful for all the opportunities that we’ve been apart of this year. From competing at the highest level and having our dancers perform on some of the biggest stages with top artists; to dancing for our community and putting on our annual showcases, it’s amazing to see all of our dancers grow together and as individuals. None of that is possible without the love and support from our CDF! So, thank you to our parents, team mom’s, instructors, TA’s, staff and most importantly our dancers! 2022 was amazing.. 2023 we’re taking it to the next level! Happy holidays and Happy New Year! 
#ChapkisDanceFamily  #chapkisdance #tourlifewithchapkis #chapkis #chapkidz #chapkisdancestudio #chapkisworldwide 🥳❤️🚀

WE’RE BACK AND READY TO TAKE ON THE NEW YEAR! 

We have so much planned for this new year and we’re looking for new dancers who are up for the challenge. Competition season is right around the corner and we’re ready to pick up where we left off! 

If you have a desire to have fun, train, compete and grow with our World Renowned dance studio, February 4th at @chapkisdancestudio is the place to be! All skill levels and ages welcomed!

We love to see growth here at @chapkisdancestudio! Our JR. ChapKidz are a perfect example of that! Last year, they competed for their first time at @officialhhi and they performed like seasoned vets. They got a taste of what it takes to prepare for a major competition. They stayed dedicated and motivated, all while most importantly, having fun! It was amazing to see them take 🥇place! It’s never too early to get started and become a champion here at @chapkisdance! If that is something you desire and wish to be apart of, join us February 4th for our mid season auditions. The family is preparing to continue the legacy. We’re just waiting for you 🫵 to join!

Our CDF Mega Crew is our most experienced team. Last year at HHI they became Silver World Medalists!👏👏👏🔥🔥🔥🔥 what an amazing accomplishment! This team, like all of our competition teams, put their blood, sweat and tears into preparing for this moment. Although they’re our most experienced team, for a lot of these dancers this was their first time competing @officialhhi World Championships. It was a battle with the world’s best dance teams & an experience we will never forget. The bonds created and the memories made will last a lifetime. If that is something you desire and wish to be apart of, join us February 4th for our mid season auditions. The family is preparing to continue the legacy and we’re just waiting for you 🫵 to join!

Another amazing year has to come to an end.. but don’t be sad because 2024 we get to do it all again!! 

We were able to accomplish so much this year! From competing at monsters dance competition (clean sweep 🧹) to competing at starbound where our little ones were able to shine! From there we made our way over to HHI USA where ChapKidz, Prophecy & CDF Mega Crew took home gold🥇! Then we went onto HHI WORLDS and our ChapKidz placed 3rd🥉in the world! 

In between all of that, we had our daily practices, open classes and masterclass trainings from several amazing choreographers that not only shared their love for dance but also very valuable knowledge. 

Lastly, our annual showcases - Under Construction and our Holiday Show were a huge success. It’s always amazing to see the growth in each and every one of our dancers. 

We try to provide more than just dance here. We want to provide a safe space, an environment that is filled with love and support and most importantly, we are family. We’re so proud of all of our dancers. Thank you for all your hard work this year. Special thanks to the parents as well. Your support and trust in us means the world. To our volunteers and team moms, and staff, you all are so appreciated! Your contributions have made a tremendous role in our successes and we can’t thank you enough. 

We love you all! See you next year! #chapkisdance #chapkisdancefamily
